<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1039937-when-the-two-older-men-first-meet-lars">When the two older men first meet, Lars tells a story about having to shoot a dog when he was a teenager. He says that his step-father was not home at the time. Would his step-father have been Trond&#39;s father? Trond&#39;s father and Lars&#39; mother were working for the underground and were lovers, I believe. Trond never saw his father again after that summer of 1948.</a>
</div>
